aces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都可以賴落砌機佬到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n砌完番黎唔識check既 <br />\n係有心就一早用正版 唔會出事先黎補獲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明顯就係雙重標準啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe972419dfcddd7ca87ac4e1155b33dd27715803","tid":89241,"uid":46766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:43:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前D撐達狗係牛CHING個POST話達哥起碼有道歉<br />\n宜家BACKUP仔都有道歉呀<br />\n原諒埋佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n盲粉係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44737997d5a6e8c63934235f304f1df07adcab59","tid":89241,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:45:23.000Z","msg":"達哥道歉加買正版，MS 無追究！<br />\nBackup 佬道歉加買版權既話達哥都唔會追究！"},{"pid":"f1f714f35b1344c5c224bfa0b02268b6ed14413e","tid":89241,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:48:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>達哥道歉加買正版，MS 無追究！<br />\nBackup 佬道歉加買版權既話達哥都唔會追究！</blockquote><br />\n達哥咪叫你地唔好搞backup佬囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S.無論如何，各位不要去Backup佬既FB攻擊佢，或者做出咩起底既行為，呢D壓力佢未必承受到。<br />\nP.S.除此之外，都收到很多網友既支持同關心，我無法一一回復，在心中，多謝你地。"},{"pid":"a9583da020e6589538756463589bb3308948b623","tid":89241,"uid":72198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:50:44.000Z","msg":"我想問backup佬有冇比返d錢，而且佢一開始話自己無營利，又要扮野，到而家都冇點交代筆錢點。高下立見！"},{"pid":"928c749eecff22121489af4e01e40108d6be4f32","tid":89241,"uid":76631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:52:36.000Z","msg":"Backup佬道左歉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad170e79fc2a1