rmal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買正版係未來用正版喎 咁過去點彌補bill叔🤔"},{"pid":"ea76b59cc085f2639ba8ed4bfbb6aae2b9e92243","tid":89241,"uid":264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:11:54.000Z","msg":"WINDOWS不是正版係因為冇入KEY冇激活啫係試用版<br />\n如果用老番破解左就唔會彈個舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"422a7cc06e86d1ea00cc9306e8f28e68806427ef","tid":89241,"uid":47639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:13:43.000Z","msg":"兩件事性質唔一樣<br />\n達哥係用翻版 唔係制造翻版 <br />\n套落今次件事度佢只係睇back up 唔睇official channel既人 根本兩件事唔可以做比較"},{"pid":"eb3942a7ed6d075a0f0bf18be61d25ae3c343457","tid":89241,"uid":46609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:13:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>道歉+買番正版<br />\n<br />\n道歉+回水<br />\n<br />\n咁依家回咗水未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n達哥回水比Microsoft未？<br />\n達哥唔洗錢就可以用翻版window搵錢，backup佬又唔洗錢可以用達哥片搵錢<br />\n<br />\n但達哥只要道歉加買正版就得唔洗回水，但backup佬就要道歉加承諾唔再搞達哥既片，而且要回水<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪雙重標準？"},{"pid":"b8a8dd3ae3f5af1dd2e6455bbb82df48efbbc16e","tid":89241,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff338b29783c6eeba6eaeb56a5f067f0f38449b","tid":89241,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:27:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都無問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本就雙重標準<br />\n你試下其他連登仔憎既youtuber好似大j呢d咁<br />\n比人踢爆用老翻再買番正版<br />\n一定照比人追擊到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地一出左事即刻道歉買番<br />\n加上話唔定係砌機佬裝<br />\n<br />\n如果個咩backup佬比人發現有錢收即刻嘔錢道歉你估仲有人狙擊佢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來砌機佬陷害達哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b49494d938ffa47985fad787ade53a350291d8a","tid":89241,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"達哥唔用windows <br />\n邊個幫佢宣傳<br />\n應該windows畀返錢達哥做代言人"},{"pid":"8d0cf7de362563566cedf534584bceb5975809ad","tid":89241,"uid":46609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:40:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>達哥唔用windows <br />\n邊個幫佢宣傳<br />\n應該windows畀返錢達哥做代言人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n神化左，已經太遲了"},{"pid":"6a555e4bd4769fe5fa3da58587f3cec65cb35f21","tid":89241,"uid":20618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:41:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>道歉+買番正版<br />\n<br />\n道歉+回水<br />\n<br />\n咁依家回咗水未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n達哥回水比Microsoft未？<br />\n達哥唔洗錢就可以用翻版window搵錢，backup佬又唔洗錢可以用達哥片搵錢<br />\n<br />\n但達哥只要道歉加買正版就得唔洗回水，但backup佬就要道歉加承諾唔再搞達哥既片，而且要回水<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪雙重標準？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n達哥有叫佢回水咩?"},{"pid":"9817d67bd53838f947ed6fcfd927e674d7c7ddf5","